The tests in `bin/tests/` seem to be missing some resources.  In particular, `./bin/tests/test_io.cpp` and `./bin/tests/test_gui.cpp` both refer to files in a `test_data` folder that does not exist.

e.g.:

./bin/tests/test_io.cpp:    RES texture = ResourceLoader::load("test_data/rock.png");
./bin/tests/test_io.cpp:    ResourceSaver::save("test_data/rock.xml",texture);
./bin/tests/test_io.cpp:        FileAccess\* z = FileAccess::open("test_data/archive.zip", FileAccess::READ);
./bin/tests/test_gui.cpp:       text->load("test_data/concave.png");
